com.buschmais.jqassistant.core.scanner.api

Interface ScannerContext

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ScannerContextImpl

    public interface ScannerContext
    Defines the context for the scanning process. Values of a specific type may be pushed/popped to provide information for plugins.
